174 A.3d 505 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. C.D., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND A.H., DEFENDANT. IN THE MATTER OF THE GUARDIANSHIP OF K.D., A MINOR—RESPONDENT.

C-170 September Term 2017

078827 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001394-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
